  "informal_statement": "Summing a function over the one-element range {0} gives its value at 0.",
  "informal_proof_idea": "`simp` reduces the single-term sum. (An initial `exact Finset.sum_range_one` left a stuck AddCommMonoid metavariable; simp resolves it.)",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem sum_range_one' (f : ℕ → ℕ) : (∑ i ∈ Finset.range 1, f i) = f 0",
